Class JMSCommandGeneratorFactory

java.lang.Object
  hjb.http.cmd.JMSCommandGeneratorFactory
public class JMSCommandGeneratorFactory
extends Object

JMSCommandGeneratorFactory is used to instantiate the various JMSCommandGenerators used by the service methods of HJBServlet.
